DTEND:20190204T172500Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>In this talk I will go in details about how we quickly resolve incidents using Prometheus and ansible.</p>

<p>Come and discover how we linked the monitoring, queuing systems and orchestration to do unattended incident management.</p>

<p>One of the main advantages of this is that we can apply technical remediation or mitigation from business metrics,
even if things happen at different levels.</p>

<p>All of this working anywhere Prometheus and ansible run, so not only in a kube env, but also in a traditional infrastructure.</p>

